# Installation

Add this to `~/.config/alacritty/alacritty.yml`

```yaml
colors:
  primary:
    background: "0x#2e3440"
    foreground: "0xc5d4dd"

  normal:
    black: "0x434c5e"
    red: "0xe1647d"
    green: "0xa3be8c"
    yellow: "0xdfc185"
    blue: "0x95b8f2"
    magenta: "0xa999f0"
    cyan: "0x8dbf9d"
    white: "0xc5d4dd"

  bright:
    black: "0x434c5e"
    red: "0xe1647d"
    green: "0xa3be8c"
    yellow: "0xdfc185"
    blue: "0x95b8f2"
    magenta: "0xa999f0"
    cyan: "0x8dbf9d"
    white: "0xc5d4dd"
```
